    ("Numerical Weather Prediction (NWP) works by:", ["only using historical weather records to find similar patterns", "solving mathematical equations governing atmospheric physics (fluid dynamics, thermodynamics) on a 3D grid from observed initial conditions", "only analyzing satellite images by eye", "random computer-generated forecasts"], 1, "Physics-based computational forecasting."),
