    ("Probabilistic forecasts express:", ["certainty about a single outcome", "the likelihood of different weather outcomes (e.g., 40% chance of rain), providing more useful decision-making information than deterministic forecasts alone", "only temperature as a single number", "only historical averages"], 1, "Quantifying uncertainty helps users make better decisions."),
