    ("Forecast verification measures:", ["only whether rain occurred", "the accuracy and skill of weather forecasts using statistical metrics like bias, root-mean-square error, and skill scores relative to climatology", "nothing useful for improving forecasts", "only user satisfaction with the forecast"], 1, "Essential for continuous model improvement."),
